      public Prescription(String prescriptionID, String patientID, String patientName, String doctorID, String doctorName, LocalDate datePrescribed, Map<String,Integer> medications, String status, String notes)
      Constructs a Prescription object with specified details.
      Parameters:
      prescriptionID - the unique identifier of the prescription
      patientID - the unique identifier of the patient
      patientName - the name of the patient
      doctorID - the unique identifier of the doctor
      doctorName - the name of the doctor
      datePrescribed - the date the prescription was issued
      medications - a map of medications and their dosages
      status - the status of the prescription (e.g., "Pending")
      notes - any additional notes related to the prescription
